text: Frigyes Gráf (born 1884, date of death unknown) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1884 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1906 Intercalated Games Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sopron
